author: markt
msg: Use chunked encoding for http 1.1 requests with no content-length (regardless of keep-alive) so client can differentiate between complete and partial responses.

author: markt
msg: Fix processing of time argument in the "Expire sessions" action in the Manager web application.

The patch also provides separate templates for different variants of a message, printed by that action. That is to allow proper translation of those messages, though I cannot provide such translation by myself. (kkolinko)
